-- Sigma Pharma Shares Climb After Citigroup Raises Recommendation to `Buy'
-- Jason Gale
-- 2010-06-17T00:43:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/sigma-pharmaceuticals-shares-gain-after-citigroup-raises-rating-to-buy-.html

          
          
             Sigma Pharmaceuticals Ltd. gained as
much as 4 percent to 51.5 Australian cents after Citigroup Inc.
raised its rating on the Melbourne-based drug company to “buy”
from “sell.”  
 The shares added 1.5 cents to 51 Australian cents on the
Australian stock exchange at 10:38 a.m. local time.  
          
          


  


        